statement from Erdogan's office.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 744, \"end\": 750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9999997780978693, \"rank\": 2.2190209178753466e-07, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}, {\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999933454531356, \"rank\": 6.5596931864805765e-06, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pope Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}, {\"begin\": 891, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999976107574, \"rank\": 2.389300853742619e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recep_Tayyip_Erdo\\u011fan\", \"score\": 0.9996957007693985, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Erdogan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recep_Tayyip_Erdo\\u011fan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recep_Tayyip_Erdo\\u011fan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Turkish leader told the pontiff in a telephone call that \\\"human dignity was being trampled on, religious and moral values were being mocked, offending Muslims as much as the Christian world,\\\" the statement said.\", \"from\": 1